[{"id":"d84d8911aad118282ec0ac1692750429","from":"Lesley Groff","from_email":"lesley@nysgllc.com","to":"J. Epstein","to_list":[{"name":"J. Epstein","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"FW: Here is the fund I just interviewed with yesterday","date":"2008-01-03T18:32:55.000Z","formatted_date":"Jan 3, 2008","formatted_time":"6:32 PM","body":" \n\n \n\nFrom: Ellen Snibbe Baker [mailto:ellensnibbebaker@yahoo.com] \nSent: Thursday, January 03, 2008 1:15 PM\nTo: Ellen Snibbe Baker\nSubject: Here is the fund I just interviewed with yesterday\n\n \n\nI'd love to hear your thoughts on this company...I went to see them\nyesterday and we are trying to explore whether this would be a good fit\nfor me and how successful I might be able to be there.  I am to call him\nnext week to set up another apt.  He is thinking about bringing me in as\na consultant for a while to see how I do.  I am so skittish since I had\nthat last false start with WP Stewart.  Your input would mean a lot to\nme.  Thanks\n\n \n\nEllen Snibbe Baker\n\n55 East 87th St., 5M\n\nNew York, New York  10128\n\n \n\nellensnibbebaker@yahoo.com\n\n \n\n646-682-9719\n\n917-304-1652 cell\n\n \n\n\"The Future belongs to those who believe in the beauty of their dreams.\"\nEleanor Roosevelt\n\n","body_html":"<html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" xmlns:w=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word\" xmlns:x=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:excel\" xmlns:m=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/2004/12/omml\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40\">\n\n<head>\n<META HTTP-EQUIV=\"Content-Type\" CONTENT=\"text/html; charset=us-ascii\">\n<meta name=Generator content=\"Microsoft Word 12 (filtered medium)\">\n<style>\n<!--\n /* Font Definitions */\n @font-face\n\t{font-family:Calibri;\n\tpanose-1:2 15 5 2 2 2 4 3 2 4;}\n@font-face\n\t{font-family:Tahoma;\n\tpanose-1:2 11 6 4 3 5 4 4 2 4;}\n@font-face\n\t{font-family:Consolas;\n\tpanose-1:2 11 6 9 2 2